snippet.title: Skullgirls Mobile (iOS & Android)
snippet.description:
Skullgirls is a 2D Fighting RPG packed with unique, colorful characters to collect, upgrade, and customize as you search for the mysterious SKULLGIRL!

Custom controls designed specifically for mobile allow you to effortlessly execute a wide variety of amazing moves and combos with a single tap or swipe. Discover deep tactical choices mixed with gameplay that’s easy to pickup and play.

Download Now!
Apple iOS: http://skullgirlsmobile.com/ios
Google Android: http://skullgirlsmobile.com/aos
